    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project lovers! This car is ready for a second chance and offers a fantastic opportunity for someone looking to roll up their sleeves and bring a vehicle back to life. While it currently needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it's a budget-friendly way to get into a classic model with plenty of potential for the right owner!",
